ProEvents
=======================================================================
ProEvents is an event reservation / booking system with unique features
not present in existing open source booking systems.

Features
=======================================================================
- Create Rooms with individual seating maps
- Let customers choose among free seats via a simple click
- Several blacklisting options for "no show" cases
- Verification via SMS

